      "patchset_number": 5,
      "line": 42,
      "message": "NB:\n\nSubscription Responses\nThe response status for subscription participants in the Create and Delete flow can be:\n\n- PENDING\n- ACCEPTED\n- REJECTED\n\nThe response depends on how the DMI Plugin responds back to NCMP.\n\nNote: The CM Subscription feature relies on DMI Plugin support for applying the subscriptions. This support is currently not implemented in the ONAP DMI Plugin.",
